    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Imitating a lesser wyvern, you hack up a ball of electrical energy and launch it. All creatures in the area of effect take 2d4 lightning damage, and must make a Reflex save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, and takes a -1 status penalty to AC against attacks from metal weapons until the end of its next turn.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, except the creature takes double damage and the status penalty to AC lasts until the end of your next turn.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d4.</p>"
